AUC scores of models

Source: R/auc_scores.R
auc_scores.Rd

Dataset auc_scores contains a subset of binary classification models results from Kretowicz and Biecek (2020).

  • model - name of model followed by a number indicating setting of hyperparameters

  • split - indicator of split

  • auc - area under the ROC curve

data(auc_scores)

Format

a data frame with 1600 rows and 3 columns.
